    "101b99ae-1cea-80ce-98bc-c1fd37d1f2a1": {
      "value": {
        "id": "101b99ae-1cea-80ce-98bc-c1fd37d1f2a1",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "总体而言,2024年中国互联网就业形势较为严峻。行业正处于深度调整期,面临诸多新挑战:"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394439,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "101b99ae-1cea-8007-824a-cc138630f879": {
      "value": {
        "id": "101b99ae-1cea-8007-824a-cc138630f879",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "宏观经济下行压力加大,疫情反复、地缘冲突等不确定性因素增多,消费需求萎缩,互联网企业营收增长乏力。裁员、降薪、缩减校招规模现象较为普遍。\n互联网流量红利殆尽,获客成本居高不下。部分互联网企业过度依赖补贴与营销,企业的可持续发展能力堪忧。\n互联网监管政策趋严,反垄断、数据安全、个人隐私保护等新规密集出台,合规经营压力骤增,进一步挤压了中小企业生存空间。\n互联网行业洗牌加剧,强者愈强,马太效应凸显。中小企业被迫转型或退出市场,新增就业岗位减少。\n互联网人才供给严重过剩。高校大量开设人工智能、大数据等专业,但企业岗位需求减少,供需错配矛盾凸显。职场新人面临\"毕业即失业\"窘境。\n互联网从业者普遍感到中年危机。35岁以上员工被视为\"高龄\"（很是真实，不知道本来就很拥挤的行业，变的及其拥挤，甚至夸张，都是资本造的孽，当然其他的行业说是没什么高龄，但赚钱也不多，总体看哪个合适不合适不好说）,跳槽难度加大。职业倦怠、身心健康等问题日益突出。\n行业薪酬体系亟待调整。前几年,互联网企业凭借高薪快速扩张,但随着业绩承压,薪资虚高问题凸显。薪酬回归理性后,行业对人才吸引力有所下降。\n大厂高管出走、创业公司倒闭等负面消息频发,行业信心备受打击。资本寒冬下创业融资困难,企业发展前景不明朗,人才流失风险加大。\n当前互联网就业的确存在一些值得关注的问题和挑战:"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394440,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "101b99ae-1cea-8031-9d67-dfa82ea44add": {
      "value": {
        "id": "101b99ae-1cea-8031-9d67-dfa82ea44add",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "行业竞争加剧,部分企业生存压力加大,裁员风波时有发生。互联网红利渐退,流量获取成本上升,一些中小企业面临较大经营困难。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394440,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "101b99ae-1cea-8098-887f-eeb8ec09332f": {
      "value": {
        "id": "101b99ae-1cea-8098-887f-eeb8ec09332f",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "从业者职业生涯不确定性增加。互联网行业瞬息万变,技术迭代速度快,从业者担心自己的知识和技能随时可能过时。部分企业重视短期绩效,忽视人才长期培养,加剧了职业焦虑。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394440,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "101b99ae-1cea-80f4-af8d-facf24acdf8f": {
      "value": {
        "id": "101b99ae-1cea-80f4-af8d-facf24acdf8f",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "薪酬泡沫渐显。前些年互联网行业薪资水平虚高,但随着行业进入调整期,收入增长乏力,甚至出现下降趋势,与生活成本上涨形成反差。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394441,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "101b99ae-1cea-805f-9543-d3f2bf18567f": {
      "value": {
        "id": "101b99ae-1cea-805f-9543-d3f2bf18567f",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "\"996\"加班文化引发质疑。过度加班导致身心健康问题,工作生活失衡,可持续性受到挑战。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394441,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "30c25764-9d67-437f-8401-85b20cb8208c": {
      "value": {
        "id": "30c25764-9d67-437f-8401-85b20cb8208c",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "灵活就业群体权益保障有待加强。平台与灵活就业者之间存在事实劳动关系认定、社保缴纳等争议,相关法律制度还不够明确。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394441,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "101b99ae-1cea-80d1-9a82-c91357515613": {
      "value": {
        "id": "101b99ae-1cea-80d1-9a82-c91357515613",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "行业发展不平衡。头部企业强者恒强,中小企业生存空间受限。不同细分领域机会差异较大,vertical领域增长乏力。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394441,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "10dba2f1-e63f-49db-9587-a02402e82e51": {
      "value": {
        "id": "10dba2f1-e63f-49db-9587-a02402e82e51",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "展望未来,互联网行业短期内仍将经历结构性调整,但从长远看前景依然广阔:"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394441,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "101b99ae-1cea-80ae-8f96-cfe5b9aacda7": {
      "value": {
        "id": "101b99ae-1cea-80ae-8f96-cfe5b9aacda7",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "国家政策支持力度加大,互联网产业作为数字经济重要组成,仍是国家鼓励和扶持的战略性新兴产业。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394441,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "67ce00b5-9e1f-4e47-93bd-854bc8a095eb": {
      "value": {
        "id": "67ce00b5-9e1f-4e47-93bd-854bc8a095eb",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "5G、人工智能、元宇宙等新技术方兴未艾,有望催生出更多创新应用场景和商业模式,为互联网就业注入新动力。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "created_time": 1726299394441,
        "last_edited_time": 1726299394448,
        "parent_id": "101b99ae-1cea-8047-a65e-eb321c7f831e",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "alive": true,
        "space_id": "03c61fc7-8ae2-451d-80f2-118e6ce2d9cd"
      },
      "role": "reader"
    },
    "b3cf8edd-3788-44b0-a8f0-41a3f55129f8": {
      "value": {
        "id": "b3cf8edd-3788-44b0-a8f0-41a3f55129f8",
        "version": 2,
        "type": "numbered_list",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "互联网下沉市场仍有巨大潜力。农村电商、社区团购等新业态有望为三四线及以下城市创造更多就业。"
            ]
          ]
        },
